+ * @IEEE80211_S1G_RPS_RAW_CHAN_UL_ACTIVITY: UL Activity subfield flag
+ * @IEEE80211_S1G_RPS_RAW_CHAN_DL_ACTIVITY: DL Activity subfield flag
